{"tid":2386280,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有冇巴打喺太子執到張黑卡","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T13:15:03.000Z","uid":189579,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"159d0f3dc5cc46ac0e1f4f530f09830d67c89e9d","tid":2386280,"uid":189579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:08:13.000Z","msg":"嗰個人就係我<br />\n其實我自己都唔係好知跌咗係邊，因為自己將張卡zip咗係銀包，可能搭巴士攞出黎嗰陣跌咗<br />\n<br />\n如果有好心人近一個禮拜有搭過42c、38、1A巴士<br />\n或者係太子、九龍城、樂富巴士站附近執到張黑色卡<br />\n<br />\n裡面有好多日本旅行相同我自己拍cover唱歌的片<br />\n<br />\n我都知好大海撈針，但希望各位手足幫幫手 感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJ5FwY0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJ5FwY0.png&h=8e99f5c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"105adab6b7fc6ad8544aca8550b7006c039b6ce1","tid":2386280,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:13:44.000Z","msg":"cheap 到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e35571aec22229022d085a82fe888da9bf7149","tid":2386280,"uid":32721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:15:03.000Z","msg":"有無打去九巴問？"}]}